plus Yoga.
RESULTS: The best results in terms of increased survival time were obtained by 
the association between neuroimmunotherapy with MLT plus IL-2 and Yoga program 
(2 years), which was significantly longer with respect to that achieved by 
supportive care alone, Yoga alone, or IL-2 plus MLT alone (1 year).
CONCLUSIONS: This study would suggest that a spiritual therapeutic approach may 
improve the survival time of untreatable metastatic solid tumor patients.

