Validation study of a scale of life quality evaluation in a group of pediatric 
patients infected by HIV.

Ferreira Dde C(1), Passos MR, Rubini Nde P, Knupp RR, Curvelo JA, dos Reis HL, 
Herdy GV.

Author information:
(1)Setor de Doenças Sexualmente Transmissíveis, Universidade Federal Fluminense. 
